{"tid":508907,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"(好樂隊介紹)日本吟唱詩人-Amazarashi","createTime":"2017-12-24T16:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T03:20:03.000Z","uid":69707,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"08ff93b727d1da0a40d60035302a512314216e93","tid":508907,"uid":69707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"香港好似無咩人識,台灣反而都幾紅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uYkZLRMI3yI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuYkZLRMI3yI&d=4NbS9aiRXH3vNngC0hareEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=45dc4829\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uYkZLRMI3yI</a><br />\n一隊你一定要留意歌詞既樂隊,每首歌都好重文學味道<br />\n第一次聽佢地既歌係2013年既歌係穴を掘っている<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B2HsdgVQ-cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB2HsdgVQ-cc&d=4NbS9aiRXH3vNngC0hareEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=d78d1dee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B2HsdgVQ-cc</a><br />\n講既係日本人既自殺文化,但重點係佢個MV個idea極度高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡黎全日本最多人自殺既自殺之森-青木原樹海,<br />\n用電腦駁上twitter不斷打印出有關&quot;我想死&quot;既tweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係咁簡單既6分鐘MV,但未試過睇MV都可以帶黎咁大衝擊感<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個MV已經成為左我TOP10之1既MV<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然,唔會單憑呢點就冠名吟唱詩人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QL3T2Nzcqcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQL3T2Nzcqcs&d=4NbS9aiRXH3vNngC0hareEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=b8925144\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QL3T2Nzcqcs</a><br />\n呢首歌係Amazarashi主唱秋田ひろむ寫比中島美嘉既一首佳作(Amazarashi都有唱過)<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成首歌好有故事性,聽完成首歌就好似睇完一篇物語咁<br />\n重點係歌詞其實無好明確話你知究竟主角想死,好多地方都留左白<br />\n比讀者自己思考,代入感好高,你有曾經想過一了百了嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後都貫徹左Amazarashi一啖屎一啖砂糖既風格"},{"pid":"875e34c84f1f85e50ad914e1395b3cbcd5defa44","tid":508907,"uid":69707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T17:18:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fD9-Xtt64aI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfD9-Xtt64aI&d=4NbS9aiRXH3vNngC0hareEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=3f67e069\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fD9-Xtt64aI</a><br />\namazarashi 光、再考<br />\n又係一首故事性好強既歌<br />\n有英文歌詞,主要講我地都係靠生命中少少既&quot;光&quot;去生存落去<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h7YpV6na7ZI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh7YpV6na7ZI&d=4NbS9aiRXH3vNngC0hareEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=d20403ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h7YpV6na7ZI</a><br />\n合理誕生在世上的我們 (2017)<br />\n首17年REMASTER既舊歌,MV仲加上左主唱呤詩<br />\n呢首歌個人認為有少少禪味,世上有好多悲劇,好多不公不義扭曲既事<br />\n但都係因果,係公道合理既,<br />\n正因為係咁我地就更加應該去愛"},{"pid":"b9022cfd938327885fd5cab6fff6b545945cde62","tid":508907,"uid":69707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"聖誕得我一個毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bc4824e196317ab3a6c8a980f2e8214d281d7d","tid":508907,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"之前睇東京喰種首ed好正"},{"pid":"47e3fd7d9e29af3bc7f076d8209ebc218fa1c0ea","tid":508907,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"睇咩亂步奇談同玩nier先識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04c301ee076d143c16f975eba3068b27413ab34","tid":508907,"uid":69707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:32:32.00